title: Bon Jovi honors high school football player who died
text:
> Entertainment Bon Jovi honors high school football player who died In this Sept. 25, 2015 photo, Warren Hills Regional High School quarterback Evan Murray looks over the Summit defense in Washington, N.J. Murray, a three-sport athlete, died after suffering an injury on the field, school officials said Saturday, Sept. 26. (Larry Murphy/Lehighvalleylive.com via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
